  "body": "### Component\n\nForge\n\n### Have you ensured that all of these are up to date?\n\n- [X] Foundry\n- [X] Foundryup\n\n### What version of Foundry are you on?\n\nforge 0.2.0 (7bc3e60 2022-07-12T00:04:40.748127213Z)\n\n### What command(s) is the bug in?\n\nforge script\n\n### Operating System\n\nLinux\n\n### Describe the bug\n\n![Example](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/57450786/178615302-fa472226-1e82-4647-b716-b7a39cf37852.png)\r\n\r\nTests and script pass successfully, but then it fails and doesn't broadcast the transactions.\r\n\r\nError is in this function:\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/foundry-rs/foundry/blob/16b4ef693624368e02e3501dd137214faf9bbe76/cli/src/cmd/forge/script/sequence.rs#L125-L143",
